1
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:03,480
If you don't want me to spill the beans,

2
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:05,360
Stop it!

3
00:00:05,360 --> 00:00:07,880
Call me brother!

4
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:10,880
How did it come to this?

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,480
Who wants to go to karaoke? Raise your hand!

6
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:16,160
Me!

7
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:18,240
Let's go!

8
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:21,720
Are you coming?

9
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:22,440
What?

10
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,640
Oh, the whole class is going.

11
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:24,640
Just thought I'd ask.

12
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,440
Just because everyone else is going, I have to?

13
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:28,080
I don't think so.

14
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:35,080
What a gloomy guy.

15
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:41,360
Huh?

16
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,360
Where are my house keys?

17
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,080
Did I leave them in the classroom?

18
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,400
Oh!

19
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,300
Crap!

20
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:53,900
I bought it yesterday and left it in there ever since.

21
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,760
Oh?

22
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,400
You're into this stuff?

23
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,640
BL, huh?

24
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,840
What? No, I'm not!

25
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:11,840
That guy's name is Kono Mizuki, right?

26
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:15,000
Doesn't look like he has any friends.

27
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:17,280
He probably won't go around blabbing about it.

28
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:21,820
Hinata!

29
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,360
What is it?

30
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,000
I...

31
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:29,400
I've remarried!

32
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,280
What?

33
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,520
Oh, come on, don't look so shocked!

34
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,800
Why didn't you tell me beforehand?

35
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,920
Ah!

36
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:38,080
They're here!

37
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,920
Come on in! Hurry!

38
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,680
Excuse me.

39
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,680
Mom!

40
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,840
Oh, hello!

41
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:48,920
Come on, hurry up!

42
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,200
Get in here!

43
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,120
That day,

44
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,920
the gloomy guy from my class

45
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,800
became my stepbrother.
